%% Indexer State Machine
%% Reflects actual code in Indexer.java
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> OFF

    OFF --> INTAKING : SuperStructure sets INTAKING
    INTAKING --> OFF : SuperStructure sets OFF

    OFF --> SHOOTING : SuperStructure sets SHOOTING
    SHOOTING --> OFF : SuperStructure sets OFF

    note right of OFF : Duty cycle = 0.0
    note right of INTAKING : Duty cycle = 0.4
    note right of SHOOTING : Duty cycle = 0.4<br>(same output as INTAKING)
